videos.description: Virginia Tech QB Josh Jackson lobs a pass into the end zone for WR Damon Hazelton, who shakes a defender to secure the touchdown catch.
videos.headline: Jackson floats pass to Hazelton for Hokies' TD

videos.description: FSU QB Deondre Francois shovels a short pass to WR Nyqwan Murray, who has the ball poked away and into the hands of Virginia Tech DB Khalil Ladler.
videos.headline: Hokies' Ladler scoops up FSU fumble

videos.description: FSU QB Deondre Francois tosses a short pass to RB Khalan Laborn, who fakes out multiple defenders and runs 37 yards into Virginia Tech territory.
videos.headline: Seminoles' Laborn jukes multiple defenders on 37-yard gain

videos.description: Seminoles QB Deondre Francois tosses a pass to WR Nyqwan Murray, who spins off a defender and somehow gets stopped at the 1-yard line.
videos.headline: FSU's Murray spins off defender on failed TD call

videos.description: College football coaching legends Bobby Bowden and Frank Beamer take the field for the coin flip before Virginia Tech vs. Florida State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bowden, Beamer take part in coin flip) 2018/09/03

videos.headline: Bowden, Beamer take part in coin flip

videos.description: Virginia Tech TE Chris Cunningham blocks FSU's Brian Johnson's punt into the air and WR Eric Kumah catches it and walks into the end zone.
videos.headline: Hokies use Beamer Ball for blocked punt TD

videos.description: Josh Jackson has thrown a touchdown pass for the Hokies, who have gotten big plays on defense and special teams to lead 17-3 at halftime.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Virginia Tech controlling Florida State at halftime) 2018/09/03 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Virginia Tech controlling Florida State at halftime

videos.description: Virginia Tech RB Steven Peoples tries to punch it into the end zone on fourth down, but Florida State comes up with a big stop.
videos.headline: Hokies' Peoples stopped at the goal line on fourth down

videos.description: Florida State RB Cam Akers takes the handoff, breaks a tackle and flies 85 yards downfield ending inside the 10-yard line of Virginia Tech.
videos.headline: FSU's Akers breaks free for long run

videos.description: Nyqwan Murray spins into space before diving for the end zone. He's called down, but replay shows a touchdown. FSU only settles for a field goal.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Murray’s should-be TD only results in FG for FSU) 2018/09/03 ESHEET ENHL

videos.headline: Murray's should-be TD only results in FG for FSU

videos.description: Florida State RB Cam Akers takes the snap and tries to hand the ball off to RB Amir Rasul, but he fumbles it as Virginia Tech recovers.
videos.headline: FSU's Rasul fumbles the handoff, Hokies recover

videos.description: Virginia Tech QB Josh Jackson tosses pass to TE Eric Kumah, who powers through multiple tackles and runs 49 yards into the end zone.
videos.headline: Hokies' Kumah muscles through tackles for TD

videos.description: As the game is coming to the end, Virginia Tech players and their fans mock Florida State's tomahawk chop as they would top the Seminoles 24-3.
videos.headline: Hokies, fans mock FSU's tomahawk chop

videos.description: Virginia Tech head coach Justin Fuente expresses how pleased he is with his team's performance on the road in their 24-3 win over Florida State.
videos.headline: Fuente says stage wasn't too big for the Hokies

videos.description: In a top 20 battle, Virginia Tech picks off Deondre Francois three times en route to a 24-3 victory against Florida State.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Hokies’ defense comes up big in win over Seminoles) 2018/09/03 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Hokies' defense comes up big in win over Seminoles
